flowRoot.flowPara: Your action bar gains the l action icon.
You may treat all bank maneuvers (7 or 9) as green maneuvers.
Your action bar gains the b action icon.
Increase your agility value by 1. If you are hit by an attack, discard this card.
When attacking with a secondary weapon that instructs you to discard it to perform the attack, do not discard it unless the attack hits.
Your upgrade bar gains the W upgrade icon.
Once per round, after you perform an action, you may perform 1 free action from an equipped Upgrade card with the "Action:" header. Then receive 1 stress token.
When defending, if you are beyond Range 2 or outside the attacker's firing arc, you may change 1 of your blank results to an e result. You can equip this card only if you have the b action icon.
You may treat all bank maneuvers (7 or 9) as green maneuvers.
